[DQR.IFRS.0126.9595] The statement Bilan Actif includes an inconsistent calculation. The sum of these child components is 20,039,808,000. The values of the addends is determined by adding the values of the child concepts with a decimal value of inf. The values reported in the financial statement in the current reporting period of 2021-12-31 should be complete if the financial statement is to be mathematically accurate and complete. The addends are calculated based on the calculation linkbase defined for Bilan Actif. If addends are missing then the calculation tree should be amended. The rule will not add dimension components as the financial statement does not include a table. If dimensions are used on the statement then add a table to ensure that the dimensions are defined correctly.
